<p>In this guide to the best laptops 2019 has to offer, we here at TechRadar have gathered up a smorgasbord of fantastic notebooks and laptops that will appeal to a broad range of people, no matter what sort of laptop you&rsquo;re looking for.&nbsp;</p><p>So, we found the <a href="https://www.techradar.com/news/mobile-computing/laptops/best-ultrabook-18-top-thin-and-lights-1054355">best Ultrabooks</a> and premium laptops, alongside the <a href="https://www.techradar.com/news/computing/apple/mac-buyer-s-guide-2015-1295725">best Macs</a>, <a href="https://www.techradar.com/news/mobile-computing/laptops/best-chromebooks-top-5-chromebooks-in-the-us-1233696">Chromebooks</a> and budget <a href="https://www.techradar.com/news/mobile-computing/tablets/windows-8-tablets-release-date-specs-and-prices-916134">Windows tablets</a>. On this page, you&rsquo;ll also find the <a href="https://www.techradar.com/news/mobile-computing/laptops/best-gaming-laptops-top-5-gaming-notebooks-reviewed-1258471">best gaming laptops</a> and <a href="https://www.techradar.com/news/mobile-computing/laptops/best-2-in-1-laptops-top-5-hybrid-laptops-reviewed-1258451">2-in-1 laptops.</a>&nbsp;</p><p>We've made sure to pack our best laptops guide with brilliant devices that cover a wide range of price points, so every budget is catered for in this list. Remember: you don't need to spend a fortune to get one of the best laptops of 2019.</p><p>All of the laptops on this list have been tested and reviewed right here at TechRadar, so you can be sure they&rsquo;re worth your time. Only the best laptops will be found here, so you won&rsquo;t find any lemons here. Plus, we included our exclusive price comparison tool, so you can make sure you&rsquo;re getting the <a href="https://www.techradar.com/news/the-best-laptop-deals">best laptop deal</a> at all times.&nbsp;</p><p>We're constantly updating this guide as well, so as soon as the newest laptops are released, we'll add them to this best laptops guide &ndash; as long as they are worthy, of course.</p><p>Our built-in price comparison tool will also automatically highlight the top deals from &nbsp;online retailers, so you can be sure you're getting the best laptops for the best price.</p><h2 id="the-best-laptops-of-2019">The best laptops of 2019:</h2><div class="inlinegallery"><div class="inlinegallery-wrap"><div class="inlinegallery-item"><span class="slidecount">Image 1 of 5</span><p class="bordeaux-image-check"><img src="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" alt="" class=" lazy-image lazy-image-loading lazyload optional-image" onerror="this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)" sizes="auto" data-normal="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" data-src="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/W8fJ6AHeWGfGCjqgxJR46n-320-80.jpg" data-srcset="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/W8fJ6AHeWGfGCjqgxJR46n-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/W8fJ6AHeWGfGCjqgxJR46n-650-80.jpg 650w" data-sizes="auto" data-original-mos="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/W8fJ6AHeWGfGCjqgxJR46n.jpg" data-pin-media="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/W8fJ6AHeWGfGCjqgxJR46n.jpg"></p></div><div class="inlinegallery-item"><span class="slidecount">Image 2 of 5</span><p class="bordeaux-image-check"><img src="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" alt="" class=" lazy-image lazy-image-loading lazyload optional-image" onerror="this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)" sizes="auto" data-normal="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" data-src="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/BsCXBWKvfnQnwjiYRVspdn-320-80.jpg" data-srcset="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/BsCXBWKvfnQnwjiYRVspdn-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/BsCXBWKvfnQnwjiYRVspdn-650-80.jpg 650w" data-sizes="auto" data-original-mos="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/BsCXBWKvfnQnwjiYRVspdn.jpg" data-pin-media="https://cdn.mos.cms.futu