l-less &lsquo;Infinity Edge&rsquo; display, this Dell XPS 13 continues to be the most popular Windows laptop in the world. What&rsquo;s more, there&rsquo;s a wide range of customization options, so you can really make the Dell XPS 13 the best laptop for your needs.&nbsp;The 2019 model doesn't bring a huge amount of improvements, but then not that much about the Dell XPS 13 needs improving. Its webcam has been placed at the top center of the screen, rather than at the bottom, which a lot of customers have been asking for. You also get a longer battery life in this year's model.</p><p><strong>Read the full review</strong>: <a href="https://www.techradar.com/reviews/pc-mac/laptops-portable-pcs/laptops-and-netbooks/dell-xps-13-1328971/review" target="_blank"><u>Dell XPS 13</u></a></p><div class="inlinegallery"><div class="inlinegallery-wrap"><div class="inlinegallery-item"><span class="slidecount">Image 1 of 3</span><figure><p class="bordeaux-image-check"><img src="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" alt="Image Credit: HP" class=" lazy-image lazy-image-loading lazyload optional-image" onerror="this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)" sizes="auto" data-normal="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" data-src="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/twtmtbXrubXdy4by7M25SX-320-80.jpg" data-srcset="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/twtmtbXrubXdy4by7M25SX-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/twtmtbXrubXdy4by7M25SX-650-80.jpg 650w" data-sizes="auto" data-original-mos="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/twtmtbXrubXdy4by7M25SX.jpg" data-pin-media="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/twtmtbXrubXdy4by7M25SX.jpg"></p><figcaption><div class="caption-text">Image Credit: HP</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="inlinegallery-item"><span class="slidecount">Image 2 of 3</span><figure><p class="bordeaux-image-check"><img src="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" alt