f you go for the larger 15-inch model. The headline Touch Bar &ndash; a thin OLED display at the top of the keyboard which can be used for any number of things, whether that be auto-suggesting words as you type or offering Touch ID so you can log in with just your fingerprint &ndash; is again included. It's certainly retained Apple's sense of style, but it comes at a cost. This is a pricey machine, so you may want to consider one of the Windows alternatives. If you're open to switching to a PC, definitely consider the XPS 13 or the excellent MateBook X Pro. But, if you're a steadfast Apple diehard, this is definitely the best laptop for you!</p><p><strong>Read the full review:</strong> <a href="https://www.techradar.com/reviews/macbook-pro-2018-with-touch-bar-13-inch">Apple Macbook with Touch Bar 13-inch (2018)</a></p><div class="inlinegallery"><div class="inlinegallery-wrap"><div class="inlinegallery-item"><span class="slidecount">Image 1 of 7</span><p class="bordeaux-image-check"><img src="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" alt="" class=" lazy-image lazy-image-loading lazyload optional-image" onerror="this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)" sizes="auto" data-normal="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" data-src="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/EGbybSRFBS4ywQHKkoRSZJ-320-80.jpg" data-srcset="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/EGbybSRFBS4ywQHKkoRSZJ-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/EGbybSRFBS4ywQHKkoRSZJ-650-80.jpg 650w" data-sizes="auto" data-original-mos="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/EGbybSRFBS4ywQHKkoRSZJ.jpg" data-pin-media="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/EGbybSRFBS4ywQHKkoRSZJ.jpg"></p></div><div class="inlinegallery-item"><span class="slidecount">Image 2 of 7</span><p class="bordeaux-image-check"><img src="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" alt="" class=" lazy-image lazy-image-loading lazyload optional-image" onerror=