 Well, it&rsquo;s amazing. Not only do you get one of the most aesthetically pleasing 15-inch laptops on the market, but it also packs one of those new Intel &nbsp;Kaby Lake G-series CPUs featuring &lsquo;discrete-class&rsquo; Radeon graphics. This means that this laptop packs serious power &ndash; even if it can get a little loud.</p><p><strong>Read the full review:</strong> <a href="https://www.techradar.com/reviews/dell-xps-15-2-in-1">Dell XPS 15 2-in-1</a>&nbsp;</p><div class="inlinegallery"><div class="inlinegallery-wrap"><div class="inlinegallery-item"><span class="slidecount">Image 1 of 8</span><p class="bordeaux-image-check"><img src="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" alt="" class=" lazy-image lazy-image-loading lazyload optional-image" onerror="this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)" sizes="auto" data-normal="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" data-src="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/AvGQ2XDnfxmywBgZ2hefyg-320-80.jpg" data-srcset="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/AvGQ2XDnfxmywBgZ2hefyg-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/AvGQ2XDnfxmywBgZ2hefyg-650-80.jpg 650w" data-sizes="auto" data-original-mos="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/AvGQ2XDnfxmywBgZ2hefyg.jpg" data-pin-media="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/AvGQ2XDnfxmywBgZ2hefyg.jpg"></p></div><div class="inlinegallery-item"><span class="slidecount">Image 2 of 8</span><p class="bordeaux-image-check"><img src="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" alt="" class=" lazy-image lazy-image-loading lazyload optional-image" onerror="this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)" sizes="auto" data-normal="https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/techradar/media/img/missing-image.svg" data-src="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nk9y9qLgTdWANT5pWdwFtg-320-80.jpg" data-srcset="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nk9y9qLgTdWANT5pWdwFtg-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Nk